videos.headline: UCLA's Charisma Osbourne drains a 3
videos.description: Charisma Osbourne turns some nice Bruins ball movement into a three-pointer vs. the Sun Devils.

videos.headline: Arizona State's Treasure Hunt knocks down a tough 3
videos.description: Treasure Hunt takes a tough three with a hand in her face and knocks it down.

videos.headline: Arizona State's Tyi Skinner drains a deep trey
